Class SnakingLocationComparer

java.lang.Object
metrocs.redistricting.SnakingLocationComparer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparator<Location>
public class SnakingLocationComparer extends Object implements Comparator<Location>, Serializable
Snaking Location will compare locations in a snaking fashion meaning if all locations are in a grid any sequential block of locations read will be contiguous.
Version:
20220103.0
Author:
Jessica Trujillo, Wiwi Veratiwi, Mike Walker, Zach Morlan, Fred Buker
